function Start()

--Nairne comments on starting hunt for List of Last Deeds
	Hydra.Wait(1.0)

	followerNairne = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("NPC_QST_SignoftheTimes_Nairne_Follower")
	local idPlayer = Hydra.ActorGetFollowTarget(followerNairne)
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(followerNairne) and Hydra.ActorIsValid(idPlayer) then
		Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(CON_FOLLOW_START, idPlayer, followerNairne)
	end
	
end
